🍴 AI Recommender – Restaurant & Recipe Website
📌 Project Overview

This project is an AI-powered recommendation system that suggests nearby restaurants and personalized recipes based on user preferences.
The goal is to make food discovery easier by combining restaurant search with AI recipe recommendations in a single platform.

🚀 Features

🔍 Restaurant Finder – Search and explore restaurants by location, cuisine, or rating.

🤖 AI Recommender – Personalized suggestions based on user taste and history.

🍲 Recipe Recommender – Discover recipes using available ingredients or diet preferences.

⭐ Favorites – Save favorite restaurants or recipes.

📱 Responsive UI – Works on desktop and mobile.

🛠️ Tech Stack

Frontend: React / HTML / CSS / JavaScript

Backend: Flask / Django / Node.js (your choice)

Database: MySQL / MongoDB / PostgreSQL

AI/ML: Python (scikit-learn, TensorFlow, or PyTorch for recommendation)

APIs: Google Places / Zomato API / Recipe API (like Spoonacular)

📂 Project Structure
ai-recommender/
│── frontend/         # Website frontend code  
│── backend/          # Backend + AI recommender system  
│── data/             # Datasets (restaurants, recipes)  
│── models/           # Trained recommendation models  
│── README.md         # Project documentation  

⚙️ Installation & Setup

Clone this repository:

git clone https://github.com/alwaysalearner1234/ai-recommender.git
cd ai-recommender


Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt


Start the backend server:

python app.py


Run the frontend:

npm start


Open in browser:

http://localhost:3000

📊 Recommendation Algorithm

Uses content-based filtering (ingredients, cuisine type).

Uses collaborative filtering (similar user preferences).

Hybrid model for better accuracy.


